The Block Australia Fans vs Faves Series 8 Episode 13

The Block is back with a Fans versus Favorites format - will the old hands prevail?

Midway through their second week of renovating, the weary contestants have another challenge on their hands. They must build a one square metre house then customise and decorate their creation. The winners pocket $5000 cash.
